sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant CLEAN as Data Cleaner (knowledge.py)
    participant FS as File System (yaml)
    participant EXT as Text Extractor (knowledge.py)
    participant S_BOT as Sales Bot (chatbot.py)
    participant P_BOT as Prospect Bot (prospect.py)
    participant LLM as AI Engine

    User->>CLEAN: Submit Custom Data
    Note over CLEAN: Deletes unapproved fields.<br>Removes extra spaces.<br>Cuts text if it is too long.
    CLEAN->>FS: Save clean text to custom_knowledge.yaml
    
    rect rgba(100, 150, 255, 0.1)
        Note over S_BOT, LLM: 1. Sales Mode 
        S_BOT->>EXT: Request Custom Data
        EXT->>FS: Read YAML & Convert to Text
        EXT-->>S_BOT: Return Text Block
        Note over S_BOT: Wraps text in:<br>--- BEGIN CUSTOM PRODUCT DATA ---
        S_BOT->>LLM: Feeds data to the AI as absolute facts.
    end
    
    rect rgba(255, 150, 100, 0.1)
        Note over P_BOT, LLM: 2. Prospect Mode
        P_BOT->>EXT: Request Custom Data
        EXT->>FS: Read YAML & Convert to Text
        EXT-->>P_BOT: Return Text Block
        Note over P_BOT: Wraps text in:<br>--- BEGIN CUSTOM PROSPECT DATA ---
        Note over P_BOT: Adds Budget and Pain Points
        P_BOT->>LLM: Feeds data to the AI as "buyer research".
    end
